data.value:
Ayubowan! (May you live long)
Whether this is your first stop, last stop, or only stop in Sri Lanka, our island capital has always been one of the world’s favourites. And from our hotel, Colombo is yours to explore.
Built upon the land where our founder once resided, this exotic metropolis we call home is where our legendary hospitality shines the brightest – a privilege we extend to the world, as we take you in with open arms.
